text: Eldyak () is a rural locality (a village) in Staroyantuzovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 46 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Eldyak
